      <title>瑞士法院判处冈比亚部长反人类罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/swiss-court-convicts-gambian-minister-of-crimes-against-humanity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，瑞士一家法院判定冈比亚前部长在前总统叶海亚·贾梅 (Yahya Jammeh) 政权下犯有危害人类罪，并判处他 20 年监禁。]]></description>
