    <item>
      <title>报告称，今年通过达里恩的儿童移民差距增加了 40%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/child-migration-through-darien-gap-up-40-this-year-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国机构周三报告称，今年迄今为止，通过达里恩差距的儿童移民数量增加了 40%，并将连续第五年创下纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/child-migration-through-darien-gap-up-40-this-year-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 13:22:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非总统在关键投票前签署有争议的健康法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/ramaphosa-signs-controversial-health-law-before-pivotal-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨(Cyril Ramaphosa)签署了一项有争议的医疗保险法案，使其成为法律，几周前他的政党将面临自三十年前上台以来最艰难的选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/ramaphosa-signs-controversial-health-law-before-pivotal-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 13:17:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
